{% extends "layouts/default.twig" %}
{% set title = "Landing page - masthead" %}
{% set pageTitle = "Message from the Vice President" %}
{% set showTitle = FALSE %}
{% set showBreadcrumb = TRUE %}

{% block masthead %}

<section class="overflow-hidden masthead">
	<div class="relative min-h-96 md--min-h-160 ">
		<div
			class="absolute block w-full h-full min-h-96 md--min-h-160 has-content--after has-gradient-bottom--after">
			<img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/4584/38588637591_0241df7a93_z_d.jpg" alt="UBC I day"
				class="object-cover w-full h-full">
		</div>
		<div class="relative flex min-h-96 md--min-h-160">
			<div class="container self-end flex-1 px-4 mx-auto">
				<h1 class="masthead__page-title decoration-startline">Message from the <span class="block">Vice
						President.</span></h1>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

{% endblock %}

{% block content %}

<div class="pb-20 my-16 has-content--before introquote--big">
	<p class="text-lead text-ubc-blue-cobalt ">Welcome to UBC! Our vision in Human Resources is to enable
		people excellence in the UBC workplace through supporting the faculty and staff, and ultimately
		students, at one of the world’s best universities for research, education, and community engagement.
		I encourage you to connect with us and learn about the services and supports we offer to faculty and
		staff (including leaders and administrators), and to the community.</p>
</div>

{% endblock %}

{% block areab %}
<p>UBC is a global centre for research and teaching, consistently ranked among the top 20 public
	universities in the world. Since 1915, UBC’s entrepreneurial spirit has embraced innovation and
	challenged the status quo. UBC encourages its students, staff and faculty to challenge convention,
	lead discovery and explore new ways of learning. At UBC, bold thinking has a place to develop into
	ideas that can change the world.</p>
<p>UBC has two main campuses (Vancouver and Kelowna), with nearly 16,000 employees working in British
	Columbia, making us one of the largest employers in the province.</p>
<p>In HR, we foster an atmosphere of respect, professionalism, and collegiality that serves as the
	foundation for an outstanding work environment at UBC.
	HR provides a wide range of services within our portfolios, all with the goal of actively
	attracting, engaging, retaining, and developing employees. We work closely with our partners in
	departments and faculties across UBC to understand their needs for strategic human resources support
	in order to provide excellence in research, teaching, and student experiences. By embracing
	innovation, collaboration and inclusion in HR policies, practices, partnerships and relationships,
	we actively support UBC’s strategic vision and plan.</p>
<p>We invite you to learn about HR and how we support equity, diversity &amp; inclusion, wellbeing,
	recruitment, learning and leadership, employee engagement, workplace health, career development,
	housing and relocation, stakeholder relationships, and benefits and pensions. If you can’t find what
	you’re looking for on our website, please call our Service Centre at 604-822-8111, and our staff
	will be happy to help answer your questions.</p>
<p class="pb-4 text-sm uppercase attribution text-grey-700 has-content--after hr--small-blue">&mdash;
	Barbara Meens Thistle</p>
{% endblock %}

